title: 𝐅𝐢𝐫𝐬𝐭 𝐊𝐢𝐬𝐬 - 𝐓𝐨𝐧𝐲 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐫𝐤 𝐇𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐜𝐚𝐧𝐨𝐧
body:
• Your first kiss with Tony would be on your terms
  • He’s tried to kiss you plenty of times before you gave in
  • He had a way with words that had any woman swooning over him
  • Most woman can’t resist his charm
  • But you were the exception
  • And he found that wildly attractive
  • It actually didn’t come about until after your first date
  • Even though he had wowed you on your first date after going all out
  • You were still a little hesitant
  • You know his track record with woman
  • You didn’t want to become just another one of Tony’s woman that he didn’t even remember the name of the next time you ran into each other
  • There was something wildly attractive about you in Tony’s eyes
  • Otherwise he wouldn’t have waited until after the first date for you to kiss him
  • It was unexpected to him
  • He was talking about something that you didn’t understand, something scientific
  • And by talking, I mean rambling
  • You tried to say his name, but he just kept going on
  • So finally, you decided to shut him up with your mouth
  • You grabbed the back of his neck and pulled his lips to yours
  • His lips were so soft against yours
  • It shut him up immediately
  • Aside from the small moan he let out because he wasn’t expecting it
  • You let the kiss linger, realizing how intoxicating his lips were
  • You pulled away, not wanting to take it any further, even though you really wanted to
  • Tony looked at you, shocked
  • He was actually lost for words
  • You never actually seen this happen
  • So you just smirked, gave him a wink and walked towards the door of his office
  • “Now, hold on a minute”
  • You raised your brow and turned around on your heel
  • Before you realized how close he was to you, his lips were on yours in a breathtaking kiss
  • “FRIDAY, lock the door please”

title: So Here’s The Skit!
body:
While updating the rest of the Avengers about his mental state after the events of the Endgame, Something unexpected happens to our favorite sorcerer, Doctor Stephen Strange. Is a Skrull just playing at his emotions, or is there something deeper going on?

Runtime: 30 Minutes

Is it a skit or a mini-movie? I’ll never know. 

Stephen Strange: Me (@vincent-cipher-cosplay)

summary: It wasn't you I came for
title: It wasn't you I came for
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2EhZIPR

by S_Horne

“I told you didn’t want to see you,” Steve said, his arms folded across his chest. The first time he’d opened his door in a week and it had to be to the last person he wanted to see.

Tony’s expression gave no reaction to the snub apart from the tensing of his lips for a brief second. Instead, he knelt down on the doorstep and peeked around Steve’s legs.

“I didn’t come to see you,” Tony said, not looking up. He clicked his fingers expectantly and Steve knew what was coming. Soon enough, there was the tell-tale patter of clawed paws tapping down the hallway and a wet nose shoved its way past Steve’s calf. “I did listen to you, for once. I came to see Dodger. Hey, buddy.”
